## Proven Example: Calendar Component CSS

This is the proven pattern from the working Calendar component:

```css
/*
 * Webflow Site Variables Used:
 * - --background-primary: Calendar background
 * - --background-secondary: Hover states
 * - --text-primary: Day numbers and labels
 * - --text-secondary: Weekday labels
 * - --border-color: Calendar border and dividers
 * - --accent-color: Selected day background
 * - --accent-text-color: Selected day text
 * - --border-radius: Calendar and button rounding
 */

/* Root element - inherit Webflow typography + default padding */
.wf-calendar {
  font-family: inherit;
  color: inherit;
  line-height: inherit;
  padding: 24px;
  --wf-calendar-cell-size: 36px;
  --wf-calendar-spacing: 4px;
}

/* Container */
.wf-calendar-root {
  padding: 12px;
  background: var(--background-primary, #ffffff);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #e5e5e5);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius, 8px);
  width: fit-content;
}

/* Header */
.wf-calendar-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  gap: 8px;
}

/* Navigation buttons */
.wf-calendar-nav-btn {
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius, 8px);
  color: var(--text-primary, #1a1a1a);
  transition: background-color 0.2s;
}

.wf-calendar-nav-btn:hover {
  background: var(--background-secondary, #f5f5f5);
}

.wf-calendar-nav-btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.3;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Day cells */
.wf-calendar-day-btn {
  width: var(--wf-calendar-cell-size);
  height: var(--wf-calendar-cell-size);
  border: none;
  background: transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius, 8px);
  color: var(--text-primary, #1a1a1a);
  font-size: 14px;
  transition: background-color 0.2s;
}

.wf-calendar-day-btn:hover {
  background: var(--background-secondary, #f5f5f5);
}

.wf-calendar-selected .wf-calendar-day-btn {
  background: var(--accent-color, #1a1a1a);
  color: var(--accent-text-color, #ffffff);
  font-weight: 500;
}

.wf-calendar-today .wf-calendar-day-btn {
  font-weight: 600;
  position: relative;
}

.wf-calendar-outside .wf-calendar-day-btn {
  color: var(--text-secondary, #737373);
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.wf-calendar-disabled .wf-calendar-day-btn {
  opacity: 0.3;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}
```

